s://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Robert-Trujillo-2000x1270-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Robert-Trujillo-2000x1270-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Robert-Trujillo-2000x1270-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>罗伯特·特鲁希略 (Robert Trujillo) 代替他的儿子泰伊 (Tye) 在墨西哥城最近的一场演出中加入了他以前的乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/suicidal-tendencies">“自杀倾向”(Suicidal Tendency)</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/metallica-72-seasons-tour-stranger-things-3426805">Metallica – “我们仍在努力解决所有这些问题”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/metallica">Metallica</a>贝斯手于 1995 年离开 Suicidal Tendency，由于儿子与另一支乐队 OTTTO 的日程安排发生冲突，他接替了乐队的贝斯手 Tye。</p><p>上周四（10 月 26 日），特鲁希略与他的老乐队在墨西哥城的 House of Vans 一起演出，挽救了局面。</p><p>曲目单中包括《Institutionalized》、《You Can&#39;t Bring Me Down》和《Send Me Your Money》。该专辑大量采用了 1990 年的《Lights…Camera…Revolution!》中的素材，这是 Suicidal Tendency 最著名的专辑之一，也是第一张以 Trujillo 担任贝斯手的专辑。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="自杀倾向 - Vans México 2023 制度化 Live House" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/mMprsQ6hCNw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="自杀倾向 - You Can&#39;t Bring Me Down 墨西哥 HOV 2023 现场直播" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/YHfborH_qJw?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="把你的钱寄给我——罗伯特·特鲁希略的自杀倾向。墨西哥城。 2023 年 10 月 26 日。" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/k_SrdTF5E-s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>自杀倾向组织感谢特鲁希略的努力，并于周六（10 月 28 日）在 Instagram 上分享的一篇帖子中写道，言语“无法表达他们的感激之情”。</p><p> “接到 Vans 的电话，我们很高兴能在墨西哥城举办 House of Vans 比赛。我们在布鲁克林的老 House of Vans 演出过两次，当然，Vans 有着悠久的历史，甚至在乐队成立之前就已经开始了。不幸的是，泰伊·特鲁希略 (Tye Trujillo) 已经与他的乐队 OTTTO 预订了演出，两个日期都无法更改。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cy6T9MRuHs4/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886